nodes.text: Enmonst Rclub was an establishment located in a seedy part of the Coruscant Underworld. It was situated right between Sleeping Rose and The Hole. A run-down sign spelled out the name in luminous Aurebesh characters.
During the Clone Wars, bounty hunter Cad Bane stayed in an apartment on the same block as Enmonst Rclub, while planning a mission to break into the Jedi Temple.
